  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age between 16 and 80

          -  clinically incomplete spinal cord injury (time since injury: chronic &gt; 1 year; acute &lt;
             3 months)

          -  ASI C or D

          -  neuropathic pain and/or motor deficits

          -  diagnosed neurological disorder, eg. stroke

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  any disease limiting training

          -  epilepsy

          -  major depression or psychosis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
